videos.description: LSU forward Naz Reid takes a pass from beyond the arc and drains a long 3-pointer vs. UNC Greensboro.
videos.headline: LSU freshman Reid nails deep 3

videos.description: LSU breaks the UNC Greensboro full-court press and Naz Reid's 3-pointer bounces on the rim before falling and he adds a free throw on the play.
videos.headline: Reid's 3 finally falls for 4-point play

videos.description: LSU's Tremont Waters makes a steal and flushes down a dunk at the other end vs. UNC Greensboro.
videos.headline: Waters steals, gets up for dunk

videos.description: LSU's Tremont Waters drives and dishes to Naz Reid on the baseline for a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Reid cuts down the baseline for 1-handed slam
